<item>
            <title>[LU-6091] FIEMAP returns empty result until stat(2)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6091</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;How to reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With a fresh mounted client or purge the cache by echo 3 &amp;gt; /proc/sys/vm/drop_caches&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For any regular file, do a open(2) with O_RDONLY, then FIEMAP ioctl without stat(2). The FIEMAP ioctl will return an empty result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
